@startuml uc-13-statediagram
title UC13 — Admin manages topic/vocabulary/tests and crawler content sync — State Diagram
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #FEFEFE
  BorderColor #333333
  FontName Helvetica
}

state "Active cached content" as Cached
state "Admin editing" as AdminEditing
state "Validating content/config" as Validating
state "Saved / published" as Saved
state "Soft-disabled" as SoftDisabled
state "Validation error" as ValidationError
state "Weekly sync scheduled" as Scheduled
state "Guardrail check" as GuardrailCheck
state "Crawling Langeek" as Crawling
state "Mapping to A1-C2" as Mapping
state "Auto-published" as AutoPublished
state "Retry pending" as RetryPending
state "Failure logged" as FailureLogged
state "Admin notified" as AdminNotified
state "Manual curation fallback" as ManualFallback

[*] --> Cached : Current active content available

Cached --> AdminEditing : Admin opens console
AdminEditing --> Validating : Submit content/test/config change
Validating --> Saved : Valid create/update/config
Validating --> ValidationError : Duplicate/missing/invalid fields
ValidationError --> AdminEditing : Fix input and resubmit
Saved --> Cached : Active content/config refreshed

Cached --> SoftDisabled : Admin confirms disable
SoftDisabled --> Cached : is_active=false; hidden from learners

Cached --> Scheduled : Weekly schedule fires
Scheduled --> GuardrailCheck : Load crawler config
GuardrailCheck --> Crawling : ToS/robots/copyright/rate limit permitted
GuardrailCheck --> ManualFallback : Crawling not permitted or legal risk

Crawling --> Mapping : Langeek reachable; parse succeeds
Crawling --> RetryPending : Langeek down or crawl error
Mapping --> AutoPublished : Topics/new words mapped to A1-C2
AutoPublished --> Cached : Publish without Admin approval

RetryPending --> FailureLogged : Retry policy applied
FailureLogged --> AdminNotified : Log source URL, reason,\nlast success, retry, cache status
AdminNotified --> Cached : Keep cached content active
ManualFallback --> Cached : Manual curation/import path

note right of GuardrailCheck
  Guardrails: ToS, robots.txt,
  copyright/licensing, and rate limits.
end note

note bottom of Cached
  Crawl failure must not remove or hide
  currently active cached learning content.
end note
@enduml
